' SD-03. UC-003 좌측 또는 우측 회피 방향 선택
' Related Use Case: UC-003. 좌측 또는 우측 회피 방향 선택
' Intent: 좌우 장애물 상태와 회피 방향 정책을 이용해 좌회전 또는 우회전 명령을 결정하는 흐름을 표현한다.
' Note: 좌우가 모두 막힌 경우 방향을 선택하지 않고 UC-005로 전환한다.

@startuml SD_03_UC003_Select_Avoidance_Direction
title SD-03 - UC-003 좌측 또는 우측 회피 방향 선택

actor "센서 입력" as Sensor
participant "RVC SW Controller" as Controller
participant "SensorState" as SensorState
participant "AutomaticCleaning" as Cleaning
participant "CleaningPolicy" as Policy
participant "AvoidanceDecision" as AvoidanceDecision
participant "MovementCommand" as MovementCommand
actor "주행 장치" as Drive

Sensor -> Controller: reportSideObstacleState(leftObstacleDetected, rightObstacleDetected)
activate Controller
Controller -> SensorState: updateSideObstacles(leftObstacleDetected, rightObstacleDetected)
Controller -> Cleaning: selectAvoidanceDirection(SensorState)
activate Cleaning
Cleaning -> SensorState: sideObstacleState()
SensorState --> Cleaning: leftBlocked, rightBlocked

alt 좌측만 막힘
    Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: select(RIGHT)
    AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: selectedDirection=RIGHT
    Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(TURN_RIGHT)
    MovementCommand --> Cleaning: turnRightCommand
    Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(turnRightCommand)
    Controller -> Drive: turnRight()
else 우측만 막힘
    Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: select(LEFT)
    AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: selectedDirection=LEFT
    Cleaning -> MovementCommand: create(TURN_LEFT)
    MovementCommand --> Cleaning: turnLeftCommand
    Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(turnLeftCommand)
    Controller -> Drive: turnLeft()
else 좌측과 우측 모두 이동 가능
    Cleaning -> Policy: avoidanceDirectionPolicy()
    Policy --> Cleaning: configuredPolicy=LEFT_FIRST or RIGHT_FIRST
    Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: selectByPolicy(configuredPolicy)
    AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: selectedDirection
    Cleaning -> MovementCommand: createTurnCommand(selectedDirection)
    MovementCommand --> Cleaning: turnCommand
    Cleaning --> Controller: commandResult(turnCommand)
    Controller -> Drive: turn(selectedDirection)
else 좌측과 우측 모두 막힘
    Cleaning -> AvoidanceDecision: markBackwardRequired()
    AvoidanceDecision --> Cleaning: backwardRequired=true
    Cleaning -> Cleaning: changeMovementStatus(BLOCKED)
    Cleaning --> Controller: noAvailableDirection()
    note right of Cleaning: UC-005로 전환
end

deactivate Cleaning
deactivate Controller
@enduml
